description:
Download Here ● http://dd.xisumavoid.com (Updated to V1.1 on 22/02/14)
Survive 10 waves of creeper attacks! Knock them into the void using your creeper beater stick before they are able to blow up and send your diamonds into the void. There will be special mobs and boss rounds and at the end of the 10 waves you will be able to pickup whatever diamonds are left. Log into the game, select your difficulty and press the start game button to begin!
Note: The game supports SSP & SMP, but recommended to play with 1-3 players
